{"tid":1435051,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登係咪實行緊信用評分系統？！","createTime":"2019-08-09T02:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T04:05:17.000Z","uid":264427,"like":11,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e9da3e4256ec7494f25a5939522171be059ba2e6","tid":1435051,"uid":264427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:45:58.000Z","msg":"有冇人發現<br />\n其實連登咁成功<br />\n係因為<br />\n起底功能有啲似信用評分<br />\n電郵登記有啲似實名登記<br />\n結果推出嚟嘅文有質素保證<br />\n當然前題係一眾巴絲本身都要高汁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n信用評份呢個concept其實係work 架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只不過畀獨裁者運用就變成咗侵犯人權同埋限制自由嘅系統<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f4afa5dd44853f94b9c95e555d7ea0cf4aef5a","tid":1435051,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63010d98ff4d0d633de149a9bb950def60746c0d","tid":1435051,"uid":293698,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:46:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad6cc7c78b9a140592f08ef7f5ed045f1783ee92","tid":1435051,"uid":43314,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:47:16.000Z","msg":"連登咁成功係因為自由"},{"pid":"6a72c4703895b5dd2d380a45b531ffaa1cf2baf3","tid":1435051,"uid":65187,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:50:16.000Z","msg":"點睇黑鏡個集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自由度高 互相評分<br />\n跟本呢樣野唔符合現實"},{"pid":"8bb5543e47c61e237dba20a47bb57f71816c3ae2","tid":1435051,"uid":66530,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:51:41.000Z","msg":"共產主義本應都係最理想既制度<br />\n<br />\n好多時唔係件事出問題<br />\n而係&rsquo;人&rsquo;"},{"pid":"1a15d7f06b9d410415444ae181a6f1a528032475","tid":1435051,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T02:52:44.000Z","msg